title: Apocalyptic Chef Awakening
description: Apocalyptic Chef Awakening Manhwa The Cook of a Perished World, Cooking Disease in a Ruined World, 멸망한 세계의 취사병 Shin Young-jun, a sergeant chef, was greeted by the apocalypse just days before vacation. The battalion turned into chaos in an instant, and the communication network was cut off. Then something appeared before his eyes! [Congratulations on your awakening!] [Job: Novice Chef Lv.1] If I had been a warrior or an assassin, I would have tried to stand alone… What was assigned to him was chef, which is obviously a support job. There’s nothing to be done if it’s like this. “From here on, I will feed you.”
alternative_titles: The Cook of a Perished World
Cooking Disease in a Ruined World
